        <Commentary>
            <ab>VrS2.10c <em>vāstrō.dataēnīm</em>] cod. Geldner, Kellens <em>vāstrō.dātainīm</em>. Cf. Skt. <em>prāvṛṣéṇya-</em> (<bibl>Debrunner, 1954</bibl>, p. 504).</ab>
            <ab>VrS2.10e <em>varšni.haršəm</em>] Kellens. Geldner <em>varšniharštəm</em>.</ab>
            <ab>VrS2.10f <em>sarəδīm</em>] cod. Gelner, Kellens <em>sarəδəm</em>. Cf. VrS1.10 <em>sarəδahe</em> instead expected <em>sarəδiiehe</em>.</ab>
            <ab>VrS2.10g <em>arətō.kərəiϑinəm</em>] Kellens <em>arətō.kərəiϑinəm</em>; Geldner <em>arətōkarəϑnahe</em>. Vid. VrS1.10.</ab>
        </Commentary>
    </Apparatus>
    <Parallels>
        <ab>VrS2.10 ≈ VrS1.10, VrS17.9, VrS25.12, VrS27.26, VrS77.9, VrS90.10.</ab>
    <ab>Without the mention of the attributes to each <em>gahanbār</em> and mentioning <em>sarəδa</em> ("year") as <em>ratu</em> ~ Y1.9, Y2.9, Y3.11, Y4.14, Y6.8, Y7.12, Y17.8, Y22.12, Y24.19, Y59.8, Y66.9, VrS78.21, VrS79.14, VrS81.8, VrS82.9.</ab>
    </Parallels>
